    <item>
      <title>特朗普和拜登在“超级星期二”获胜，以重新匹配很少有人想要的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/trump-tightens-grip-on-nomination-with-virginia-tenn-nc-wins</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登总统和唐纳德·特朗普总统将在大选中重赛，很少有美国人对此感到兴奋，而华尔街的捐助者也徒劳地试图避免。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/trump-tightens-grip-on-nomination-with-virginia-tenn-nc-wins</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 01:12:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>什么是“非 Dom”税收身份以及英国为何取消它？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/what-is-uk-non-dom-status-why-is-it-controversial-quicktake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣杰里米·亨特 (Jeremy Hunt) 在周三的预算声明中宣布，英国政府正在以基于居住权的新安排取代允许富裕外国人少缴税的“非居留”制度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/what-is-uk-non-dom-status-why-is-it-controversial-quicktake</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 17:24:33 GMT</pubDate>
